name: Tim Walz
tweet: The lowest unemployment rate since the turn of the century and more Minnesotans entering the labor force shows that our economy is strong.  But there's more we can do, starting with direct payments up to $1,000 per couple and $500 per individual. Let's get this done.

name: Tim Walz
tweet: 12 years ago the Affordable Care Act was signed into law, reducing costs and increasing the quality of health care for Minnesotans. Now we’re working to build on its successes to create a better, more affordable health care system.
